ZH: 机理是指事物运行的原理和规律。
EN: The mechanism refers to the principles and laws of how things work.

ZH: 这个装置的机理非常复杂，需要深入研究。
EN: The mechanism of this device is very complicated and requires further investigation.

ZH: 专家们正在研究这种新药物的机理。
EN: Experts are studying the mechanism of this new drug.

ZH: 我们需要了解火灾蔓延的机理。
EN: We need to understand the mechanism of how fires spread.

ZH: 这种机械设备的工作机理非常清晰。
EN: The working mechanism of this mechanical device is very clear.

ZH: 光合作用是植物生长的重要生理机理之一。
EN: Photosynthesis is one of the important physiological mechanisms for plant growth.

ZH: 沉降是地质学中重要的地质作用机理之一。
EN: Sedimentation is one of the important geological processes in geology.

ZH: 这个物质的分解机理还有待进一步研究。
EN: The mechanism of decomposition of this substance still needs further study.

ZH: 长城的建造机理被视为古代工程学的杰作。
EN: The construction mechanism of the Great Wall is considered a masterpiece of ancient engineering.

ZH: 其实，我们对宇宙诞生的机理还知之甚少。
EN: In fact, we know very little about the mechanism of the birth of the universe.

ZH: 这部设备采用了最先进的技术和机理。
EN: This equipment utilizes the most advanced technology and mechanism.

ZH: 破碎机的工作机理是通过机械力将物料打碎。
EN: The working mechanism of the crusher is to crush materials using mechanical force.

ZH: 环境变化对生物群落的影响有着复杂的生态机理。
EN: Environmental changes have complex ecological mechanisms that impact biological communities.

ZH: 能量转换的物理机理在物质交换过程中起着关键作用。
EN: The physical mechanisms of energy conversion play a key role in material exchange processes.

ZH: 机理的研究有助于我们更好地理解自然界的运作规律。
EN: Studying mechanisms helps us better understand the laws of nature.

ZH: 疾病的发生机理要依靠医学研究来解析。
EN: The occurrence mechanism of diseases needs to be analyzed through medical research.

ZH: 新技术的应用机理需要经过实验验证才能确认。
EN: The application mechanism of new technologies needs to be confirmed through experimentation.

ZH: 人体免疫系统的防御机理是复杂而多样的。
EN: The defense mechanism of the human immune system is complex and diverse.

ZH: 生物学家们正在研究这种细菌抗药性的机理。
EN: Biologists are studying the mechanism of antibiotic resistance in these bacteria.

ZH: 贸易战的起因和机理令人担忧。
EN: The causes and mechanisms of trade wars are worrying.
